Package: rudder-policy-templates
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Configuration management and audit tool -  policy templates
 Rudder is an open source configuration management and audit solution.
 .
 This package contains policy templates, which are configuration models,
 adapted to a function or a particular service. By providing parameters to these
 templates, you can create configuration rules to manage nodes using Rudder
 (nodes are machines with the rudder-agent package installed).
